{
 "cells": [
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "e1a90d0b",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "# \ud83d\udcb2 \u0110\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 M\u00f4 h\u00ecnh Nh\u1eadn di\u1ec7n H\u00fat thu\u1ed1c (AI Smoking Detection)\n",
    "\n",
    "Notebook n\u00e0y th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n c\u00e1c b\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 chuy\u00ean s\u00e2u v\u1ec1 hi\u1ec7u n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00f4 h\u00ecnh **CNN + MobileNetV2** \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c fine-tune. C\u00e1c n\u1ed9i dung bao g\u1ed3m:\n",
    "1. **\u0110\u1ed9 ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c (Accuracy & Loss)** tr\u00ean t\u1eadp ki\u1ec3m th\u1eed (Test set).\n",
    "2. **Ma tr\u1eadn nh\u1ea7m l\u1eabn (Confusion Matrix)** v\u00e0 **B\u00e1o c\u00e1o ph\u00e2n lo\u1ea1i (Classification Report)**.\n",
    "3. **Ki\u1ec3m tra th\u1eddi gian th\u1ef1c thi (Inference Time Benchmark)**.\n",
    "4. **Ph\u00e2n t\u00edch \u01b0u nh\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec3m** v\u00e0 ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u00e1p ti\u1ebfp c\u1eadn."
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "id": "78a9c45b",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "import os\n",
    "import sys\n",
    "import time\n",
    "import numpy as np\n",
    "import pandas as pd\n",
    "import matplotlib.pyplot as plt\n",
    "import seaborn as sns\n",
    "import tensorflow as tf\n",
    "from sklearn.metrics import classification_report, confusion_matrix\n",
    "from tensorflow.keras.preprocessing.image import ImageDataGenerator\n",
    "\n",
    "# Th\u00eam th\u01b0 m\u1ee5c g\u1ed1c v\u00e0o path \u0111\u1ec3 import model.py\n",
    "sys.path.append(os.path.dirname(os.getcwd()))\n",
    "from src.model import create_model\n",
    "\n",
    "print(f\"Tensorflow Version: {tf.__version__}\")"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "e305fbc2",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 1. Thi\u1ebft l\u1eadp v\u00e0 T\u1ea3i m\u00f4 h\u00ecnh (Load Model)\n",
    "\n",
    "Ch\u00fang ta t\u1ea3i m\u00f4 h\u00ecnh v\u1edbi tr\u1ecdng s\u1ed1 t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e3 l\u01b0u trong qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh huấn luy\u1ec7n."
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "id": "2da94821",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "WEIGHTS_PATH = os.path.join(\"..\", \"logs\", \"smokers_classification_model_checkpoint.weights.h5\")\n",
    "IMG_SIZE = (224, 224)\n",
    "CLASS_NAMES = ['not_smoking', 'smoking']\n",
    "\n",
    "if not os.path.exists(WEIGHTS_PATH):\n",
    "    print(f\"[L\u1ed6I] Kh\u00f4ng t\u00ecm th\u1ea5y Weights t\u1ea1i: {WEIGHTS_PATH}\")\n",
    "else:\n",
    "    # Kh\u1edfi t\u1ea1o model (c\u1ea5u tr\u00fac CNN + MobileNetV2)\n",
    "    model = create_model(input_shape=(IMG_SIZE[0], IMG_SIZE[1], 3), num_classes=2)\n",
    "    # Load tr\u1ecdng s\u1ed1\n",
    "    model.load_weights(WEIGHTS_PATH)\n",
    "    print(\"[SUCCESS] \u0110\u00e3 t\u1ea3i m\u00f4 h\u00ecnh th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng!\")"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "f2a89c10",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 2. Chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb d\u1eef li\u1ec7 ki\u1ec3m th\u1eed (Test Data)\n",
    "\n",
    "S\u1eed d\u1ee5ng `ImageDataGenerator` v\u1edbi h\u00e0m ti\u1ec1n x\u1eed l\u00fd chu\u1ea9n c\u1ee7a MobileNetV2."
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "id": "b1a7d32c",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "TEST_DIR = os.path.join(\"..\", \"dataset_split\", \"test\")\n",
    "BATCH_SIZE = 32\n",
    "\n",
    "test_gen = ImageDataGenerator(\n",
    "    preprocessing_function=tf.keras.applications.mobilenet_v2.preprocess_input\n",
    ")\n",
    "\n",
    "test_images = test_gen.flow_from_directory(\n",
    "    directory=TEST_DIR,\n",
    "    target_size=IMG_SIZE,\n",
    "    class_mode='categorical',\n",
    "    batch_size=BATCH_SIZE,\n",
    "    shuffle=False # C\u1ea7n False \u0111\u1ec3 Confusion Matrix kh\u1edbp v\u1edbi Class Names\n",
    ")\n",
    "\n",
    "print(f\"Class indices: {test_images.class_indices}\")"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "d4a90123",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 3. \u0110\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 t\u1edng quan (Accuracy & Loss)"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "id": "c5a91234",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "print(\"[*] \u0110ang \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 tr\u00ean t\u1eadp Test...\")\n",
    "results = model.evaluate(test_images, verbose=1)\n",
    "print(f\"\\n\ud83d\udcc8 Test Loss: {results[0]:.4f}\")\n",
    "print(f\"\ud83c\udfaf Test Accuracy: {results[1]*100:.2f}%\")"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "a5a94321",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 4. Ma tr\u1eadn nh\u1ea7m l\u1eabn (Confusion Matrix)\n",
    "\n",
    "Ghi nh\u1eadn l\u1ea1i c\u00e1c tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n \u0111\u00fang v\u00e0 l\u1ed7i sai s\u00f3t (False Positive/Negative)."
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "id": "d6a95678",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "y_true = test_images.classes\n",
    "preds = model.predict(test_images, verbose=1)\n",
    "y_pred = np.argmax(preds, axis=1)\n",
    "\n",
    "cm = confusion_matrix(y_true, y_pred)\n",
    "\n",
    "plt.figure(figsize=(8, 6))\n",
    "sns.heatmap(cm, annot=True, fmt='d', cmap='Blues', \n",
    "            xticklabels=CLASS_NAMES, \n",
    "            yticklabels=CLASS_NAMES)\n",
    "plt.title('Confusion Matrix - Smoking Detection')\n",
    "plt.ylabel('Th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf')\n",
    "plt.xlabel('D\ud83d\udcb2 d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n')\n",
    "plt.show()\n",
    "\n",
    "print(\"\\n--- Classification Report ---\")\n",
    "print(classification_report(y_true, y_pred, target_names=CLASS_NAMES))"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "f8a97890",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 5. Th\u1eddi gian th\u1ef1c thi (Inference Time)\n",
    "\n",
    "\u0110o l\u01b0\u1eddng th\u1eddi gian trung b\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ec3 x\u1eed l\u00fd m\u1ed9t b\u1ee9c \u1ea3nh (Latency)."
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "id": "b9a98901",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "num_samples = 50\n",
    "sample_images, _ = next(test_images)\n",
    "single_sample = np.expand_dims(sample_images[0], axis=0)\n",
    "\n",
    "# Warm-up (ch\u1ea1y trước để GPU/CPU s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng)\n",
    "model.predict(single_sample, verbose=0)\n",
    "\n",
    "start_time = time.time()\n",
    "for _ in range(num_samples):\n",
    "    _ = model.predict(single_sample, verbose=0)\n",
    "end_time = time.time()\n",
    "\n",
    "avg_time = (end_time - start_time) / num_samples\n",
    "print(f\"\u23f1\ufe0f Th\u1eddi gian x\u1eed l\u00fd trung b\u00ecnh (1 \u1ea3nh): {avg_time * 1000:.2f} ms\")\n",
    "print(f\"\ud83d\ude80 FPS t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u1ee9ng: {1/avg_time:.1f} FPS\")"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "c1a99012",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 6. Ph\u00e2n t\u00edch Ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u00e1p & \u01afu nh\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec3m\n",
    "\n",
    "### \ud83d\udcd8 Ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u00e1p \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1\n",
    "1. **Accuracy**: Th\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111o c\u01a1 b\u1ea3n, ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi t\u1eadp d\u1eef li\u1ec7u t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ed1i c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng.\n",
    "2. **Precision/Recall**: Quan tr\u1ecdng để tr\u00e1nh b\u00e1o \u0111\u1ed9ng gi\u1ea3 (False Positive - kh\u00f4ng h\u00fat nh\u01b0ng b\u00e1o l\u00e0 h\u00fat).\n",
    "3. **Inference Latency**: \u0110\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o m\u00f4 h\u00ecnh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u1ea1y Real-time tr\u00ean camera.\n",
    "4. **Grad-CAM (\u0110\u00e3 t\ud83d\udcb2ch h\u1ee3p trong App)**: Gi\u00fap gi\u1ea3i th\u00edch AI \u0111ang nh\u00ecn v\u00e0o \u0111\u00e2u (\u0111i\u1ebfu thu\u1ed1c, kh\u00f3i, hay tay ng\u01b0\u1eddi).\n",
    "\n",
    "### \u2705 \u01afu \u0111i\u1ec3m\n",
    "- **Nh\u1eb9 v\u00e0 Nhanh**: Nh\u1edd base MobileNetV2, m\u00f4 h\u00ecnh cực kỳ tối \u01b0u cho thi\u1ebft b\u1ecb di \u0111\u1ed9ng/IoT.\n",
    "- **\u0110\u1ed9 nh\u1ea1y cao**: Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ph\u00e2n bi\u1ec7t t\u1ed1t c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i t\u01b0\u1ee3ng d\u1ea1ng thanh m\u1ea3nh (nh\u01b0 b\u00fat, ng\u00f3n tay) v\ud83d\udcb2i \u0111i\u1ebfu thu\u1ed1c nh\u1edd preprocessing n\u00e2ng cao (CLAHE).\n",
    "- **\u0110\u1ed9 th\u00fac \u0111\u1ea9y s\u1eb5n c\u00f3**: S\u1eed d\u1ee5ng Transfer Learning gi\u00fap h\u1ed9i t\ud83d\udcb2 nhanh v\u1edbi \u00edt d\u1eef li\u1ec7u h\u01a1n.\n",
    "\n",
    "### \u274c Nh\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec3m\n",
    "- **\u0110\u1ed9 ph\u00e2n gi\u1ea3i thấp**: MobileNetV2 nh\u1eadn 224x224, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 b\u1ecf l\u1ee1 c\u00e1c chi ti\u1ebft r\u1ea5t nh\u1ecf c\u1ee7a kh\u00f3i ở xa.\n",
    "- **Ph\u1ee5 thu\u1ed9c \u00e1nh s\u00e1ng**: Trong \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n qu\u00e1 t\u1ed1i ho\u1eb7c cháy s\u00e1ng, ma tr\ud83d\udcb2n nh\u1ea7m l\u1eabn c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u0103ng False Positive do bóng \u0111\u1ed5.\n",
    "\n",
    "### \ud83d\udca1 \u0110\u1ec1 xu\u1ea5t\n",
    "- **YOLO integration**: N\u1ebfu mu\u1ed1n tracking nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u00f9ng l\u00fac.\n",
    "- **Temporal analysis**: S\u1eed d\u1ee5ng LSTM/Transformer \u0111\u1ec3 ph\u00e2n t\u00edch h\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9ng \u0111\u01b0a tay l\u00ean mi\u1ec7ng th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf thay v\u00ec ch\ud83d\udcb2 xem \u1ea3nh tĩnh.\n"
   ]
  }
 ],
